{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01XbtW5LGAR2HDuD7HGtxJh7","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information you requested. Here's a complete summary of both files:\n\n## App.tsx - Router Structure and Hooks\n\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx`\n\n### Provider Stack (lines 26-40):\n```tsx\nexport function App() {\n  return (\n    <BrowserRouter>\n      <PriceFeedProvider>\n        <PlayerProfileProvider>\n          <QuestsProvider>\n            <BossRaidProvider>\n              <AppContent />\n            </BossRaidProvider>\n          </QuestsProvider>\n        </PlayerProfileProvider>\n      </PriceFeedProvider>\n    </BrowserRouter>\n  );\n}\n```\n\n### Router Structure (lines 366-384):\n- Home: `/` → HomePage\n- Game routes with error boundaries for: `/coinflip`, `/lord-of-rngs`, `/close-call`, `/crash`, `/game-of-trades`\n- Game round proof pages: `/coinflip/:matchId/proof`, `/lord-of-rngs/:matchId/proof`, `/close-call/:roundId`\n- User features: `/profile`, `/loot`, `/quests`, `/fairness`\n- **Referral capture**: `/r/:code` → ReferralCapture\n- Fallback: `*` → NotFoundPage\n\n### ReferralCapture Component (lines 450-461):\n```tsx\nfunction ReferralCapture() {\n  const { code } = useParams<{ code: string }>();\n  if (code) {\n    try {\n      localStorage.setItem(\"referral_code\", JSON.stringify({ code, capturedAt: new Date().toISOString() }));\n    } catch {\n      // localStorage may be unavailable (private browsing, storage full) — proceed with redirect\n    }\n  }\n  return <Navigate to=\"/\" replace />;\n}\n```\n\nThe component:\n- Extracts the referral `code` from the URL param\n- Stores it in localStorage with a timestamp\n- Silently handles localStorage failures (private browsing, etc.)\n- Redirects to home page (`/`)\n\n---\n\n## referral-api.ts - Complete API Client\n\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/lib/referral-api.ts`\n\n### Response Types:\n- `ReferralCodeResponse` - code + url\n- `ApplyReferralResponse` - referrer + benefit\n- `ReferralStatsResponse` - counts, volumes, earnings (referredCount, activeCount, totalVolumeLamports, totalEarnedLamports, pendingLamports)\n- `ReferralEarningItem` - per-game earning log (roundId, gameType, refereeWallet, wagerLamports, earnedLamports, createdAt)\n- `ReferralEarningsResponse` - paginated items with pagination metadata\n- `ClaimResponse` - claimId, amountLamports, status (\"pending\" | \"completed\" | \"failed\"), txSignature\n\n### API Functions:\n\n1. **setReferralCode(token, code)** - POST `/referral/code` - Create/update own code\n2. **getReferralCode(token)** - GET `/referral/code` - Fetch own code\n3. **applyReferralCode(token, code)** - POST `/referral/apply` - Link to referrer\n4. **getReferralStats(token)** - GET `/referral/stats` - Summary stats\n5. **getReferralEarnings(token, page?, limit?)** - GET `/referral/earnings?page=X&limit=Y` - Paginated log\n6. **requestReferralClaim(token)** - POST `/referral/claim` - Start async claim (returns 202)\n7. **pollClaimStatus(token, claimId)** - GET `/referral/claim/{claimId}` - Check claim status\n\n### Auth & Helpers:\n- All calls require JWT Bearer token from `useSession().accessToken`\n- Base URL from env: `VITE_FAIRNESS_BACKEND_URL` (defaults to `http://127.0.0.1:3100`)\n- Common error handling: throws descriptive error messages from backend"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: ae99d28c45606be27 (use SendMessage with to: 'ae99d28c45606be27' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 43552\ntool_uses: 6\nduration_ms: 24786</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6e340fd0-3e08-4923-9328-61b8592b2652","uuid":"f5d932dc-77d8-48d7-bfd7-2370878c38fa","timestamp":"2026-03-25T13:00:32.021Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read these files in full and provide their complete contents:\n1. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/pla